OL,3,CMeet the tortoise who was recycled and
OL,4,Csurvived a spiked barrel drum
OL,6,FA tortoise has "miraculously" been
OL,7,Frescued with only minor injuries after
OL,8,Fsurviving several recycling processors
OL,9,Fand a 15-foot drop.
OL,11,FThe animal has been named after
OL,12,FMayside Recycling Centre in Guernsey,
OL,13,Fwhere he was eventually found in a
OL,14,Fblue recycling bag.
