OL,3,CMeet the tortoise who was recycled and
OL,4,Csurvived a spiked barrel drum
OL,6,FSteve Byrne, GSPCA Manager, adds: "We
OL,7,Fhave seen some amazing rescue stories
OL,8,Fat the GSPCA, but this really is
OL,9,Fincredible.
OL,11,F"How the tortoise got into the
OL,12,Frecycling we may never know, but
OL,13,FMayside is incredibly lucky to have
OL,14,Fsurvived his ordeal.
OL,16,F"We really can't put into words how
OL,17,Flucky he is ... He is in miraculously
OL,18,Fgood condition."
