OL,3,CMeet the tortoise who was recycled and
OL,4,Csurvived a spiked barrel drum
OL,6,FThe tortoise is now on the road to
OL,7,Frecovery, getting the all clear from
OL,8,Fhis X-rays and receiving anti-
OL,9,Finflammatory pain medication.
OL,11,FThe GSPCA hopes that he was not thrown
OL,12,Faway intentionally and is appealing
OL,13,Ffor help to track down the tortoise's
OL,14,Fowner so they can be reunited.
OL,16,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,17,Fcall 01481 257261.
